name: Blog
body:
### Welcome to my blog

This is my blog, it reflects my and only my point of view, but, since I'm usually right you can agree with me, worshiping is allowed but it is usually a bad idea and you don't have to tell me about it. You disagree? This is your right, don't let anybody tell you otherwise but I'd like to ear about it, might learn something.
